Cognizant Technology Solutions is aware of the desire to shift business processes to digital technologies and it wants to help. To help customers make the switch, the information technology outsourcing company provides intelligent systems, automation, cloud technologies, and cyber security tools. Cognizant also offers digital services and solutions, consulting, application development, systems integration, application testing, application maintenance, infrastructure services and business process services. The company targets companies in financial services, health care, manufacturing, retail, and logistics as well as communications and media. Most of Cognizant's software development centers and employees are in India. Most of the company's revenue is generated in North America.
